1. set up a virtual environment for the project
      python -m venv jackmanimation_website_env
2. set the environment going
3. install Django 3
      pip install "django>3,<4"
4. create a default django project
      django-admin startproject jackmanimation_site
5. step into the site directory
      cd jackmanimation_site
6. create a database for the site
      python manage.py migrate
7. run the server to confirm it is all ok
      python manage.py runserver
8. Will the server is running go to http://127.0.0.1:8000 and check it out 
